* Deterministic first-pass device models for the host simulator.
* These are simplified behavioral models, not vendor production models.

.model REVERSE_DIODE D(Is=1e-12 N=1.02 Rs=0.01 Cjo=20p)
.model TVS_SMAJ16A D(Is=1e-12 N=1.1 Rs=0.05 Bv=17.8 Ibv=1m Cjo=500p)
.model LED_RED D(Is=2e-18 N=2.0 Rs=2 Cjo=20p)
.model LED_GREEN D(Is=2e-20 N=2.1 Rs=2 Cjo=20p)
.model LED_BLUE D(Is=1e-22 N=2.2 Rs=2 Cjo=20p)
.model OPEN_DRAIN SW(Ron=5 Roff=1e12 Vt=0.5 Vh=0.05)
.model HARNESS_CONTACT SW(Ron=0.001 Roff=1e12 Vt=0.5 Vh=0.05)
